        <body>
            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><ab><lb n="1"/>
                <expan><abbr>L</abbr><ex>ucius</ex></expan> Turpilius <supplied reason="lost"><expan><abbr>L</abbr><ex>uci</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>f</abbr><ex>ilius</ex></expan></supplied> <lb n="2"/><expan><abbr>Cam</abbr><ex>ilia</ex></expan> Maximus et T<supplied reason="lost">urpilia</supplied> <lb n="3"/>Maximina <expan><abbr>fil</abbr><ex>ia</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>schol</abbr><ex>am</ex></expan> co<supplied reason="lost">llegi</supplied> <lb n="4"/>fecerunt quam vi ignis am<supplied reason="lost">issam</supplied> <lb n="5"/><expan><abbr>colleg</abbr><ex>ium</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>fabr</abbr><ex>um</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>p</abbr><ex>ecunia</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>s</abbr><ex>ua</ex></expan> res<supplied reason="lost">tituit</supplied>
            </ab></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Die Tafel besteht aus mehreren zusammengehörigen Fragmenten. Da sie vermauert ist, nur 1,5 cm Tiefe meßbar. (A): falsche Reihenfolge der Buchstabenhöhe. (B): Z. 3: AE: f(ilia) statt fil(ia); Z. 5: AE, Mennella - Cresci Marrone: fab(rum) statt fabr(um). Erwähnung der schola fabrum von Pisaurum in CIL XI 6335.</p>
            </div>
